name: MultiPad
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: MultiPad is a community-governed decentralized multi-chain powered launchpad, enabling upcoming promising projects to raise funds. MultiPad will also partner with these projects and help them with marketing, go-to-market strategies, technical advice and assistance wherever needed.
